{"tid":2460012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[真人真事] 返工撞到共享女人巨星曾恩怡","createTime":"2021-03-24T13:59:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-25T11:30:14.000Z","uid":60535,"like":27,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fb631819a394c886c6d2dcc97ee7223f192a3778","tid":2460012,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T13:59:33.000Z","msg":"是咁的，件事大概係2個月前左右，由於我冇睇共享女人嘅關係，事前喺真喺我唔識香港嘅共享女人。<br />\n<br />\n小妹是做酒店reception嘅，有一日，曾恩怡出現喺大堂個lobby，而我就喺唯一一個企緊counter，佢就行埋嚟問我嘢，我重申一次，我嗰刻真的不知道曾恩怡是誰。<br />\n<br />\n我 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n曾恩怡 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 有咩可以幫到你？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 有冇得睇下你哋個ball房<br />\n心諗乜撚嘢ball房呀屌你老母，冇受過教育？<br />\nBallroom就Ballroom啦，我記得嗰時係夜晚9點幾同個ballroom有event做緊，佢嗰樣仲要好撚臭寸<br />\n再加上睇ballroom喺要搵event sales預約時間先可以睇，唔撚喺話睇就睇，你估你喺大明星？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 唔好意思小姐，我哋而家個ballroom有event進行緊，如果要睇嘅話(比咗張酒店卡片佢)，可以同我哋event sales預約返個時間呀。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 下？你哋而家冇sell屎咩？<br />\n屌你，9點幾收撚哂工啦，嗰腦裝屎？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 𠵱嗰時間都多數已經收哂工架啦。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 哈，咁準時呀，咁你叫你經理出來，你幫唔到我。<br />\n嗰一刻已經好想一巴車落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 好呀，請問小姐貴姓呢？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 我喎！(佢指著自己個樣)<br />\n心諗who the fuck are you? 我再問<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 小姐貴姓？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 你叫你經理出嚟啦，你經理會識得我。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : 請你等等。<br />\n<br />\n最正喺。。。我經理。。。唔識講廣東話，黑人嚟，亦都冇睇過連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經理 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : Good evening madam, how may I help you?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Er... I want see ballroom.<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : I am very sorry that there&rsquo;s an event on going in the ballroom which is quite impossible to show you. But you may contact our event sales associate for any further questions. (又比張酒店卡片佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> : <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Thank you<br />\n佢望一望經理，望一望張卡片，再望一望我，之後就走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後經理問我佢邊位，我話我都唔識佢，之後我都係問同事先知道佢原來喺曾恩怡。"},{"pid":"331f195a9e073e590c499fed80bcd963f9d1fb3e","tid":2460012,"uid":177089,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T14:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmSYELmE1KuwDwEX8Buxfs1k8XPMSc9Vwo3AVGmS3aPza7?filename=x2i0jQw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2i0jQw.jpg&h=7345054f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻？"},{"pid":"e11cc2848b3e48851e5ea39027f48ca914f89dab","tid":2460012,"uid":60535,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"331f195a9e073e590c499fed80bcd963f9d1fb3e","tid":2460012,"uid":177089,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T14:02:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x2i0jQw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx2i0jQw.jpg&h=7345054f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢隻？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T14:03:38.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />差啲俾佢屈"},{"pid":"7b6c00e12d30916de41d0b18da8fc3862c1543d7","tid":2460012,"uid":38904,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T14:05:35.000Z","msg":"係=是<br />\n例：我係真絲<br />\n<br />\n喺=在<br />\n例：我住喺半山"},{"pid":"28d2fe9551d09929be2c28957e26bbe4aeb4a740","tid":2460012,"uid":100581,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"睇完成篇文都唔知邊個係曾恩怡"},{"pid":"14b559f5b761c5ee859893c11ffe3cac62544c58","tid":2460012,"uid":390224,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T14:09:34.000Z","msg":"經理 ：<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWwxUNRaf1yTNNqW9oHYkarGmR1TFRFQSqDjvn4MQK3aw?filename=k6MUpjo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk6MUpjo.jpg&h=a02dc923&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ae2b292ccc37ef51c844ac8ec2044c1ed7f7d803","tid":2460012,"uid":60535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14b559f5b761c5ee859893c11ffe3cac62544c58","tid":2460012,"uid":390224,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T14:09:34.000Z","msg":"經理 ：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k6MUpjo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk6MUpjo.jpg&h=a02dc923&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T14:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10b93fe4852301f6d81a5925f7630598f0ecd244","tid":2460012,"uid":84102,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T14:44:02.000Z","msg":"垃圾共享女人，人老珠黃俾狗吊，ball你老母房 水房我就識"},{"pid":"6877a6e44f372e425d6e305234f95e7bea7f6276","tid":2460012,"uid":20029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-24T14:45:13.000Z","msg":"搵唔到ig"},{"pid":"29f92ab7d1b1a07dae019